{
  "stem": "471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- eventually, we were all four together here, in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was our goal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't survive for too long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One die of lung cancer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One die of a-- of a heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And still, you know, it was always a woman behind it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to talk about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one had also, cancer of the bone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was-- the last one was in 1975.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here, when that brother was dying, my wife after 23 year, she ask me for a divorce.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, wait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let me go through to the tragedy first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And believe you me, I'm not a gambler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm not a womanizer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not a drunkard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was a strictly 101% a family man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All I want is my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's bottom line.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It going to be-- to be bad?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They caught me in the street and put them on a big truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tow me all the way to Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pustkow, this is after-- after Tarnow, in a camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they start to beat us there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over there, we start to build barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those barracks is supposed to be for the prisoners of war, Russian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is by December, 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pustkow is a forest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's nothing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they used to beat us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No food, cold, from the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother didn't even know what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have no idea what was going on at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- the-- the few hundred young fellows in the middle of the street, I remember like today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, under there they-- they have a-- a-- a-- oh, what do they call that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what you call it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
